Eddie Lampert

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Edward Lampert)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Eddie Lampert


Born
Edward Scott Lampert
(1962-07-19) July 19, 1962 (age 55)
Roslyn, New York, US


Nationality
American


